Quarter - once in 3 months - Fiscal/financial Year FY, 4 quarters , 
Season planning 


Under agile - devops model, create a bug —> 

Feature request —> create a feature in the board with all the details —> assigned to dev —> send for approval to test and deploy —> testing —> deployed —> monitored —> deployed to staging env —> deployed to production env
Conitunous integration and continously deployed 



Code - source code 

Local machine - developers own system —> laptop or a desktop
